body_html:
@WenguoLi I see you closed on the recommendation to try "try --inference_type=FLOAT".

I have the exact same issue: it works for a float model, but not for a quantized model (--inference_type=QUANTIZED_UINT8).

The float model is too slow for me, and adding --default_ranges_min=0 and --default_ranges_max=255 makes the model unusable because of the low accuracy.

I'm retraining a custom image set from a quantized model ssd_mobilenet_v1_quantized_coco from the model zoo.

@andrehentz any ideas how to go forward?
